job.title: IACS Assistant Recruitment 2021 –Apply inline for Various Posts
job.body:
Total Vacancies: Various

Name of the post:

  • Project Assistant and Institute Fellow

Description:

Indian Association for the Cultivation of Science issued a total of various vacancies for the posts of Project Assistant and Institute Fellow . The online application for these posts under IACS shall start from 18-03-2021 The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before 14.04.2021. For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these posts is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The application fee for IACS Assistant Recruitment 2021:

  • Mode of application: Online
  • For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 18-03-2021
  • The Last date to apply online is 14.04.2021

Educational qualification:

You must have the degree in B.S / B/Tech to apply for the post of Project Assistant and Institute Fellow

Age limit criteria:

  • The minimum age required to apply: 18 YEARS
  • The maximum age required to apply is: 28 YEARS
  • For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

Pay Scale:

  • The pay scale as per 7th pay commission for the post of Project Assistant and Institute Fellow is: Rs10,000 per month
  • Check the detailed notification also something has missed.

How to apply for IACS Assistant Recruitment 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of IACS 
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of Project Assistant and Institute Fellow
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs. 

Download official notification
